ENTRY            M0034   20260105   20260226   20260226       M143
SUBENT        M0034001   20260105   20260226   20260226       M143
BIB                 10         21
TITLE      Search for 2+ states in 4He by photodisintegration
           method
AUTHOR     (Yu.M.Arkatov,P.I.Vatset,V.I.Voloshchuk,V.N.Gur'ev,
           V.A.Zolenko,I.M.Prokhorets)
INSTITUTE  (4UKRKFT)
REFERENCE  (J,SNP,31,157,1980) English translation of
           (J,YF,31,297,1980)
FACILITY   (LINAC,4UKRKFT)
INC-SOURCE (KINDT)
DETECTOR   (TRD)
COMMENT    It was shown that a 2+ state with energy
            Eg = 30 - 35 MeV and with g**2 = 5 MeV may exist
            in He-4 nucleus.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical errors only
HISTORY    (19820216C)
           (19910202A) Corrected by V.Varlamov, V.Mclane.
           (20130524A) Corrected by V.Varlamov: INSTITUTE,
            FACILITY, INC-SOURCE, (ERR-S), dates, REACTION in
            SUBENTs 004-006, lowercase.
           (20260105U) Corrected by VV and SD:
            small corrections in all SUBENTs.
ENDBIB              21
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           24
SUBENT        M0034002   20260105   20260226   20260226       M143
BIB                  4         10
REACTION   (2-HE-4(G,N)2-HE-3,,POL/DA,,ASY/MSC)
           Angular anisotropy coefficient as ratio of coeff. a/b
            from fit angular distribution in form:
              a*sin**2(theta)+b*sin**2(theta)cos(theta)+
              c*sin**2(theta)cos**2(theta)+d
ANG-SEC    (ANG1,N)
           (ANG2,N)
STATUS     (CURVE,,Yu.M.Arkatov+,J,SNP,31,157,1980)
            Data from Fig. 1.
HISTORY    (20260105U) Corrected by VV and SD: STATUS.
ENDBIB              10
COMMON               2          3
ANG1       ANG2
ADEG       ADEG
         0.       180.
ENDCOMMON            3
